Phase 1: Core Architecture & Base Components

1. Base Infrastructure (2 weeks)
   - Design new proxy architecture
   - Implement modular component system
   - Create interface definitions
   - Set up testing environment
   - Develop deployment scripts

2. Core Modules (3 weeks)
   └── TokenBase
       ├── Enhanced ERC20 functionality
       ├── Module registry
       ├── Upgrade mechanisms
       └── Event system

3. Security Framework (2 weeks)
   └── SecurityModule
       ├── Multi-signature system
       ├── Time-lock mechanisms
       ├── Emergency pause
       ├── Access control
       └── Rate limiting